{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji12.pdf"],"article":{"title":"和抗大第三期毕业学员的谈话","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"和抗大第三期毕业学员的谈话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年9月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们到抗大来学习，有三个阶段，要上三课：从西安到延安八百里，这是第一课；在学校住窑洞，吃小米，出操上课，这是第二课；现在第二课上完了，但是最重要的还是第三课，这便是到斗争中去学习。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1938,"month":9}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":451,"page_end":451},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"对话"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}